{"type": "article", "id": 23809, "title": "水泥建筑花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143213LDz3aJpPBZHgtTxO.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个水泥做的方形花瓶灵感源于 1970 年代“东德”的建筑。它的表面被划分成排列整齐的小格子，上面刻有浮雕似的纹理，用深浅颜色来表现门和窗，将原本很单调的建筑形式运用其中，表现出雕塑的极简美，也有一点怀旧。它也可以用做放汤匙等容器。每一个花瓶都是手工做的，经过了防水处理，售价 100 美元，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/wbs-70/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061432119rqKaDuZEsxFiLR0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143212WoLaQD5hMBxV3JGr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143213qx7WDuNnAmYUTMLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}